```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int a = 6;
int b = 4;
int c = 9;
if (a > b || b > c)
{
    System.out.println("P");
}
if (a < c && b > 2)
{
    System.out.println("Q");
}
if (!(a == b))
{
    System.out.println("R");
}
```

