Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int x = 7;
int y = 3;

if (x > 5)
{
    y += x;
}

if (y > 10)
{
    x -= 2;
}

if (x + y == 15)
{
    y++;
}

System.out.println(x + " " + y);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int points = 4;
boolean bonus = false;

if (points > 5)
    bonus = true;
    points += 2;

if (bonus)
    points += 10;

System.out.println(points);
```
